	<h2>Our Story</h2><br>
	<p> This time my trip to home was a different experience. I went around my father’s farm. I saw a lot of cucumber (organically grown) ripened but not yet plucked and sold to market. I asked my father why we are not selling this. His response was “If you get it to market you will get 3 Rs and they sell it for 25 to 30 Rs. You won’t get even the transportation cost."
	</p>
